      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs must be traceable to measurement data or certified material specifications; input uncertainty must be characterized.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties sourced from ASTM F136 and manufacturer certificates of conformance. Screw geometry from CMM measurements of production implants (n=3). UHMWPE block properties from literature with ±10% bounds. Input uncertainty propagated through screening sensitivity study; total input uncertainty contribution to QoI uncertainty estimated at 3.2%."
