      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test samples must be production-representative implants with documented lot traceability; sample size must support statistical comparison.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested: n=6 at Lab 1 (FDA OSEL), n=5 at Lab 2 (DePuy Synthes). All from same production lot (Lot 2021-NC-75). CMM verification of 3 samples confirmed dimensional conformance. Sample size supports paired comparison with E/uval metric."
    },
    {
