      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions must replicate COU loading environment; multiple load levels or configurations should be tested to bound model validity domain.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 standard test configuration applied at single load level (monotonic ramp to 40 mm displacement). Only one test condition evaluated; dynamic or fatigue loading not included in this COU. This factor falls below required level (achieved 2, required 3). Accepted as known limitation because the COU is explicitly scoped to static compression-bending only, consistent with the regulatory submission scope."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
