      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA input parameters must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental test conditions; any discrepancies must be quantified and their effect on QoI bounded.",
      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions (UHMWPE block fixation, actuator displacement control, load cell placement) replicated in FEA model. Block geometry measured and matched to FEA geometry. Actuator compliance characterized and incorporated. Equivalency confirmed for all three QoIs."
    },
    {
