      "rationale": "E/uval computed for all three QoIs: stiffness 1.41, yield force 1.63, force at 40 mm 0.98. All satisfy E/uval < 1.96. Percentage differences also within 10% pre-specified bound. Comparison performed independently at both laboratories with consistent results. Achieved level 4 reflects multi-laboratory corroboration."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
